{"tid":952590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐嚇16歲女索裸照 已婚神學生囚10月","createTime":"2018-12-23T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T10:15:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c62e6753bce651ffd49d8a16bd43dcada84a9d1a","tid":952590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181220/20572964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F20572964&d=Ne99BDIxKz%2BAP7GrYjwHry7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=09344835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F20572964&h=45786495\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181220/20572964</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月20日 <br />\n<br />\n恐嚇16歲女索裸照<br />\n已婚神學生囚10月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181220/large/17264307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F17264307.jpg&h=30df371d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已婚神學生兩度威脅女童追加拍到性器官的新裸照，法庭昨炮轟他行為卑鄙，判即時入獄10個月。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】已婚神學生瞞妻上網結識未成年少女，發展地下婚外情並成功向女童索取裸照後，兩度威脅女童追加拍到性器官的新裸照，否則舊裸照會寄到女童學校及放上網。現已退學的被告早前認罪，法庭昨炮轟他行為卑鄙，判即時入獄10個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告周北權（31歲）早前承認兩項刑事恐嚇、一項促致他人製作兒童色情物品，及一項管有兒童色情物品罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官︰須嚴肅處理卑鄙行為<br />\n<br />\n周北權手機內藏19張事主裸照及6段裸體影片，顯示16歲女事主擺出色情姿勢。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官徐綺薇昨判刑指，案情非常嚴重，心理報告認為被告再犯機會屬中等偏高，法庭有責任保護未成年的無知少女。被告不止一次威嚇將事主裸照發送到她就讀學校，令事主受驚嚇及精神痛苦，法庭須嚴肅處理被告的卑鄙行為，否則鼓勵他人模仿，使不道德風氣繼續蔓延。她拒絕判緩刑，認為全無阻嚇效用。<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述被告精神科報告時透露，被告早於13歲已拍拖及有性經驗。求情指被告上網交友原想紓壓，結識事主後，事主曾自願及主動向被告傳送裸照；被告自知鑄成大錯，因本案喪失學業兼留案底，已是很大懲罰，其妻則希望輕判以讓被告繼續做好爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC2499/18<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n大孖腦手術後康復　與妹入住院舍"},{"pid":"7fc616be29ad3a34be309cb56e825b9e9ea7ff79","tid":952590,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"信仰的力量"},{"pid":"95311361d416c41790f38b916aa4edb83b532479","tid":952590,"uid":57504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"主內互勉"},{"pid":"64d281a823af16007fb30ce8d2e688b814fc8f21","tid":952590,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98e4284cd4db4285e700d2d99e9c282415c0a326","tid":952590,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256a259d0495b86711aeab0e50b4ab62feaf6d7c","tid":952590,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64d281a823af16007fb30ce8d2e688b814fc8f21","tid":952590,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"神學學生"},{"pid":"f9260a7a813327d3c26ba796e4fd0739ba912fe8","tid":952590,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14209e983cdd4d27d18ea5bf886415a9eaa51eaa","tid":952590,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"屌埋都淨係告收藏"},{"pid":"6443e050f1308e89ab428fe952debd9845294153","tid":952590,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"讀壞腦"},{"pid":"d719b8bf6f14d044dd111d2d1180958cec7556eb","tid":952590,"uid":11555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cdc9604d37c2e57f14e5e7b50b7de73efde387","tid":952590,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"10 個月太輕"},{"pid":"214e4cc3a8db